1
00:00:14,533 --> 00:00:16,533
I will give you anything
you want.

2
00:00:16,667 --> 00:00:20,033
Please, don't hurt our baby.
Give her back!

3
00:00:20,167 --> 00:00:21,433
Anything I want?

4
00:00:21,567 --> 00:00:25,433
I will give your baby back
if...

5
00:00:25,567 --> 00:00:29,767
You give me Amanda in exchange
for your daughter.

6
00:00:29,900 --> 00:00:31,033
Deal?

7
00:00:31,167 --> 00:00:33,367
- We need to alert the police.
- That's a good idea.

8
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:35,300
Let the police deal
with your mom.

9
00:00:35,467 --> 00:00:36,800
You can't report it
to the police.

10
00:00:36,933 --> 00:00:38,567
She might hurt Chloe.

11
00:00:38,700 --> 00:00:41,433
But once they find her,
she can't do anything.

12
00:00:41,567 --> 00:00:42,633
She'll be captured.

13
00:00:42,767 --> 00:00:45,333
She chose to use violence.
We should do the same.

14
00:00:45,467 --> 00:00:46,567
And then what?

15
00:00:46,700 --> 00:00:48,567
Are we going to corner Rina?

16
00:00:48,700 --> 00:00:49,933
What if she hurts the child?

17
00:00:50,067 --> 00:00:53,133
What if she plans to kill
the baby no matter what we do?

18
00:00:53,267 --> 00:00:55,033
Please, don't say that.

19
00:00:55,167 --> 00:00:58,033
I know how Rina thinks.

20
00:00:58,167 --> 00:01:00,000
Why are you being like this?

21
00:01:00,133 --> 00:01:02,367
Why are you making us lose hope?

22
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,633
We don't even get
to see Chloe yet.

23
00:01:04,767 --> 00:01:05,800
Stop it.

24
00:01:05,933 --> 00:01:08,333
That's enough. You don't need
to argue.

25
00:01:08,500 --> 00:01:10,367
There's only one solution
to this problem.

26
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:11,833
I'll go to Rina.

27
00:01:11,967 --> 00:01:15,267
We will give her what she wants
in exchange for your child.

28
00:01:15,400 --> 00:01:17,500
Mom, I'm afraid you'll get hurt.

29
00:01:17,633 --> 00:01:19,167
I want our family
to be together.

30
00:01:19,300 --> 00:01:23,000
You, Red, and Chloe.
I can't let you do this, Mom.

31
00:01:23,133 --> 00:01:27,000
Yen, I'm sorry. It's my fault
that your family isn't together.

32
00:01:27,133 --> 00:01:29,267
If only I'd forgiven Rina

33
00:01:29,400 --> 00:01:32,033
and moved on with my life
with Lucho.

34
00:01:32,167 --> 00:01:34,500
Mom, it's Rina
who couldn't forgive.

35
00:01:34,633 --> 00:01:35,900
Not you.

36
00:01:36,033 --> 00:01:38,333
I will talk to her. I will
ask her for forgiveness.

37
00:01:38,467 --> 00:01:40,667
I'll ask her to stop
this revenge.

38
00:01:40,833 --> 00:01:42,600
So no one else will get hurt.

39
00:01:42,733 --> 00:01:46,700
I need to do that so everyone
can have a peaceful life.

40
00:01:46,833 --> 00:01:49,967
I won't let you put
your life at risk!

41
00:01:50,100 --> 00:01:51,533
You need protection!

42
00:01:51,667 --> 00:01:54,200
You don't need to kill anyone
for me.

43
00:01:54,333 --> 00:01:56,200
Lucho, I'm grateful to you.

44
00:01:56,333 --> 00:01:58,333
You support everything
I want to do.

45
00:01:58,467 --> 00:01:59,667
But this is enough.

46
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:01,800
We have to stop getting revenge.

47
00:02:01,933 --> 00:02:05,733
We have to stop using violence.
It won't do us anything good.

48
00:02:05,867 --> 00:02:07,067
You will face Rina?

49
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,567
Are you going to be okay?

50
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:10,500
Are you all okay with this?

51
00:02:10,633 --> 00:02:13,433
I don't know why we got
to this point.

52
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,833
Why did she hurt me like this?

53
00:02:15,967 --> 00:02:18,200
She betrayed me.

54
00:02:18,333 --> 00:02:19,933
Why did she do this to me?

55
00:02:20,067 --> 00:02:22,400
Why?

56
00:02:24,367 --> 00:02:28,200
I can't let Amanda deal
with that crazy woman alone.

57
00:02:28,333 --> 00:02:31,100
You know what Rina did
to that midwife, right?

58
00:02:31,233 --> 00:02:33,000
What else can she do

59
00:02:33,133 --> 00:02:35,700
once she's faced with her
mortal enemy?

60
00:02:35,833 --> 00:02:37,367
But what about the baby?

61
00:02:37,500 --> 00:02:38,633
What about Amanda?

62
00:02:38,767 --> 00:02:40,200
She's my only concern.

63
00:02:40,333 --> 00:02:42,367
I love her so much, Dindi.

64
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:44,133
I waited a long time for her.

65
00:02:44,267 --> 00:02:46,033
I thought we would
never be together.

66
00:02:46,167 --> 00:02:48,633
But destiny has allowed us
to cross paths again.

67
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:51,167
I still can't believe
she's my wife now.

68
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:55,833
I will do everything
to defend her.

69
00:02:55,967 --> 00:02:57,900
To protect her.

70
00:02:59,667 --> 00:03:02,500
I can't lose her, Dindi.

71
00:03:02,633 --> 00:03:03,833
I can't!

72
00:03:50,233 --> 00:03:52,033
Mom.

73
00:03:52,167 --> 00:03:53,233
Our baby!

74
00:03:53,367 --> 00:03:56,767
Our visitors have arrived, baby.

75
00:03:59,333 --> 00:04:00,633
Chloe...

76
00:04:00,767 --> 00:04:03,033
Don't you dare come here, Eden.

77
00:04:03,167 --> 00:04:04,367
You're not the one I want!

78
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:09,167
Give me Amanda, or else
you won't see your child!

79
00:04:25,700 --> 00:04:28,433
Rina, I'm here now.
I'll come with you!

80
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,400
Mom, no!

81
00:04:30,533 --> 00:04:31,433
Mom...

82
00:04:31,567 --> 00:04:34,467
- Don't try to intervene, Eden.
- Mom, please.

83
00:04:34,600 --> 00:04:37,667
Mom, please, just give us
our baby back.

84
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:38,633
Rina!

85
00:04:38,767 --> 00:04:40,333
We did what you asked.

86
00:04:40,467 --> 00:04:41,167
We didn't call the police!

87
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:43,133
Just take the baby and run!

88
00:04:44,467 --> 00:04:46,233
Mom, please.

89
00:04:46,367 --> 00:04:48,167
No one should get hurt anymore.

90
00:04:48,300 --> 00:04:49,467
You can be free again.

91
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,767
No! Free? Me?

92
00:04:51,900 --> 00:04:53,700
I will be on the run
my whole life

93
00:04:53,833 --> 00:04:55,500
because the police won't stop
chasing me.

94
00:04:55,633 --> 00:04:56,867
That's how things
will end up for me.

95
00:04:57,000 --> 00:05:00,300
But you know what? I don't mind.

96
00:05:00,433 --> 00:05:03,233
As long as I get
revenge for Angelo.

97
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:05,833
I just want to kill Amanda!

98
00:05:05,967 --> 00:05:07,533
Okay, fine!

99
00:05:07,667 --> 00:05:10,533
We had an agreement, right?
That's why I'm here.

100
00:05:10,667 --> 00:05:12,033
I'm here now.

101
00:05:13,633 --> 00:05:15,633
Put your gun down.

102
00:05:15,767 --> 00:05:16,900
What now, Eden?

103
00:05:17,033 --> 00:05:18,733
Do you have a hard time
which one to choose?

104
00:05:18,867 --> 00:05:20,233
Let me have Amanda,

105
00:05:20,367 --> 00:05:22,767
or else you won't ever see
your child again!

106
00:05:22,900 --> 00:05:24,733
- Mom, no! Please, Mom!
- Mom, no!

107
00:05:25,867 --> 00:05:27,100
Rina!

108
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:32,367
Please, leave the baby out
of this!

109
00:05:32,500 --> 00:05:33,800
Put the gun down.

110
00:05:33,933 --> 00:05:36,333
Please, give them
their child back.

111
00:05:37,933 --> 00:05:38,900
No, no, no!

112
00:05:39,033 --> 00:05:41,067
- I'll come with you!
- Mom!

113
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:42,267
Let her go!

114
00:05:42,400 --> 00:05:44,467
Come here, Amanda.

115
00:05:51,833 --> 00:05:53,633
Lord, first of all,

116
00:05:53,767 --> 00:06:00,200
I thank you for keeping
Eden's child alive.

117
00:06:00,333 --> 00:06:02,633
Because you protected her

118
00:06:02,767 --> 00:06:06,267
even though she's been away
from her parents.

119
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:11,233
But the child's life
is in danger again.

120
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:16,900
I'm begging you,
please save her again.

121
00:06:17,033 --> 00:06:19,933
Save our family.

122
00:06:21,333 --> 00:06:25,500
Please, keep Amanda
and Eden away from harm.

123
00:06:36,967 --> 00:06:38,600
Raul! No!

124
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:49,867
Angelo?

125
00:06:52,267 --> 00:06:54,867
Angelo!

126
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,433
Angelo!

127
00:06:58,467 --> 00:07:01,800
They'd been through so much.

128
00:07:01,933 --> 00:07:03,733
Think about your life!

129
00:07:03,867 --> 00:07:05,667
Your future!

130
00:07:06,933 --> 00:07:08,367
Leave!

131
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,367
Auntie, no!

132
00:07:10,500 --> 00:07:11,500
Let's go, Eden.

133
00:07:11,633 --> 00:07:12,700
Let's go home.

134
00:07:12,833 --> 00:07:14,633
Come on, let's go home!

135
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:17,733
- I don't want to go home!
- Let's go!

136
00:07:17,867 --> 00:07:21,033
Let's go home.

137
00:07:22,233 --> 00:07:23,800
Mom!

138
00:07:28,967 --> 00:07:32,200
They suffered a lot.

139
00:07:33,667 --> 00:07:37,900
We must keep on fighting
for the truth.

140
00:07:38,033 --> 00:07:41,200
Mom, you will be out of here one
day.

141
00:07:42,467 --> 00:07:46,700
And we will be together again.

142
00:07:50,333 --> 00:07:54,067
And they hurt each
other many times.

143
00:07:55,100 --> 00:07:57,100
Stay away from Red.

144
00:07:57,233 --> 00:07:58,667
You have to forget he exists.

145
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,800
Mom, I love him.

146
00:08:00,933 --> 00:08:03,000
Then you have to endure
the pain!

147
00:08:03,133 --> 00:08:05,533
I can't forgive you
for what you did.

148
00:08:07,767 --> 00:08:10,433
Forget that I'm your mother!

149
00:08:10,567 --> 00:08:13,100
I don't want to do that, Mom!

150
00:08:13,233 --> 00:08:17,567
Mom, I love you so much.
Please, don't make me choose.

151
00:08:17,700 --> 00:08:19,700
You love me?

152
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,533
Then do as I say.

153
00:08:24,600 --> 00:08:31,567
Give them a chance
to heal together.

154
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:37,333
At least now we know the truth.
That's what matters.

155
00:08:39,033 --> 00:08:41,933
We will get your baby back.

156
00:08:44,167 --> 00:08:47,433
And our family will be complete.

157
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:57,567
No one can ruin our relationship
anymore.

158
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,667
I promise you that.

159
00:09:04,167 --> 00:09:07,733
Okay, Mom. Me too, I promise.

160
00:09:07,867 --> 00:09:09,033
I'm sorry.

161
00:09:09,167 --> 00:09:13,333
- I love you so much, Eden.
- I love you so much too!

162
00:09:14,900 --> 00:09:17,700
Please, give Eden a chance

163
00:09:17,833 --> 00:09:21,200
to become a great mother
to her child.

164
00:09:21,333 --> 00:09:27,067
And give Amanda a chance
to care Eden and her child.

165
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,467
You look stunning, dear.

166
00:09:29,633 --> 00:09:30,567
Mom.

167
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:33,667
Another thing that makes you
more radiant

168
00:09:33,800 --> 00:09:36,200
is the happiness within you.

169
00:09:36,333 --> 00:09:38,000
Thank you, Mom.

170
00:09:38,133 --> 00:09:40,233
After everything we've
been through,

171
00:09:40,367 --> 00:09:44,033
I only want to be a part
of your beautiful life.

172
00:09:44,167 --> 00:09:48,400
Finally, one of my dreams
is about to come true.

173
00:09:48,533 --> 00:09:51,567
Too bad our baby's not
with us anymore.

174
00:09:52,767 --> 00:09:54,500
I wish she was here with us.

175
00:09:56,300 --> 00:09:57,667
Let's just be grateful

176
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,700
that you and Red
are still alive.

177
00:10:00,733 --> 00:10:02,633
You can still make
a lot of children.

178
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:05,033
You can build your own family.
Right?

179
00:10:05,167 --> 00:10:07,000
You guys are still young.

180
00:10:08,867 --> 00:10:13,033
Their safety and future
are in your hands now.

181
00:10:14,333 --> 00:10:17,200
You didn't abandon them before.

182
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:20,833
I know you also will not
fail them today.

183
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:26,567
I trust you, Lord.

184
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:35,567
One...

185
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:40,333
Two...

186
00:10:42,100 --> 00:10:44,633
I won't let you win, Rina.

187
00:10:45,700 --> 00:10:48,767
I won't let you have Amanda!

188
00:10:55,667 --> 00:10:57,967
I'm not going to run.

189
00:10:58,100 --> 00:10:59,267
Run, Amanda!

190
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:02,567
Our baby!

191
00:11:02,700 --> 00:11:03,633
Lucho!

192
00:11:03,767 --> 00:11:06,567
The baby!

193
00:11:06,700 --> 00:11:08,300
Hurry, hurry!

194
00:11:15,767 --> 00:11:17,600
Run! Don't let the baby
get hurt!

195
00:11:35,067 --> 00:11:36,400
Lucho!

196
00:12:09,167 --> 00:12:13,567
No!

197
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:15,300
Lucho!

198
00:12:32,867 --> 00:12:35,467
- Dad.
- Red, my mom.

199
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:37,367
Lucho!

200
00:12:40,333 --> 00:12:41,767
You're evil!

201
00:12:41,900 --> 00:12:44,633
You don't need
to kill him!

202
00:12:44,767 --> 00:12:46,667
That's what he gets
for getting in the way!

203
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:49,133
You're a meddler, Lucho!

204
00:12:49,300 --> 00:12:51,333
Lucho!

205
00:12:51,467 --> 00:12:53,200
Lucho!

206
00:12:57,867 --> 00:12:59,033
- My mom.
- Yen!

207
00:12:59,167 --> 00:13:01,100
Red.

208
00:13:01,233 --> 00:13:02,333
Yen!

209
00:13:11,133 --> 00:13:13,267
Don't hurt my mom.

210
00:13:15,333 --> 00:13:17,367
Don't you dare, Eden!

211
00:13:17,500 --> 00:13:18,233
Come here!

212
00:13:18,367 --> 00:13:19,667
No!

213
00:13:19,800 --> 00:13:21,567
Let my mom go!

214
00:13:21,733 --> 00:13:22,700
Let's see what you can do.

215
00:13:22,833 --> 00:13:24,033
Go on!

216
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,467
You can't do it, right?

217
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,667
You can't save your mom.

218
00:13:29,800 --> 00:13:31,433
Let her go!

219
00:13:31,567 --> 00:13:33,833
You want me to let her go?
Put your gun down!

220
00:13:35,267 --> 00:13:38,600
- Stop it, Rina!
- Shut up! Be quiet!

221
00:13:39,900 --> 00:13:42,800
What now? Can't you pull
the trigger, Eden?

222
00:13:42,933 --> 00:13:45,433
Can't you save your mom?

223
00:13:45,567 --> 00:13:46,933
I knew it. Put that down!

224
00:13:47,067 --> 00:13:48,900
I can!

225
00:13:49,033 --> 00:13:50,933
Dad!

226
00:13:59,833 --> 00:14:03,333
I can do it for my child's sake,
who you almost killed!

227
00:14:03,467 --> 00:14:05,100
I can do it for my mom!

228
00:14:05,233 --> 00:14:07,300
Oh, really? Can you kill me?

229
00:14:07,433 --> 00:14:08,867
- Can you kill me?
- Let her go!

230
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:10,767
- Are you sure?
- Put the gun down, Eden!

231
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:12,133
That's not who you are!

232
00:14:12,267 --> 00:14:13,867
You're not capable
of taking revenge.

233
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:16,867
Don't make your hands dirty.
Put the gun down.

234
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:18,400
- Put that down.
- Go to your daughter.

235
00:14:18,533 --> 00:14:19,633
Listen to her.

236
00:14:19,767 --> 00:14:21,800
You're a good daughter, right?
Put the gun down.

237
00:14:21,933 --> 00:14:23,533
Put that down!

238
00:14:24,767 --> 00:14:27,467
- Put it down!
- Put the gun down, Eden.

239
00:14:29,633 --> 00:14:31,400
You have to choose.

240
00:14:31,533 --> 00:14:33,800
Are you going to put
the gun down or not?

241
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:37,400
Put it down.

242
00:14:39,133 --> 00:14:41,300
You're all talk!
Put the gun down.

243
00:14:41,433 --> 00:14:43,600
I know you can't do it.
Put it down!

244
00:14:47,367 --> 00:14:48,767
Kick the gun away from you!

245
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:51,100
Kick it!

246
00:14:53,233 --> 00:14:55,133
I'm glad you still know how
to obey me.

247
00:14:55,267 --> 00:14:56,433
Let's go, Amanda.

248
00:14:56,567 --> 00:14:57,600
- Mom.
- Get out of the way!

249
00:14:57,733 --> 00:14:58,967
Get out of the way!

250
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,133
Let's go.

251
00:15:06,033 --> 00:15:07,567
Yen.

252
00:15:08,933 --> 00:15:10,567
- Mom.
- Shut up!

253
00:15:10,700 --> 00:15:11,633
Mom!

254
00:15:11,767 --> 00:15:13,133
Don't hurt my mom!

255
00:15:13,267 --> 00:15:14,800
Be quiet!

256
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:36,900
Yen!

257
00:15:43,067 --> 00:15:44,900
Yen! Stay here.

258
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,567
I'm going to call the police.

259
00:15:57,700 --> 00:16:01,200
You can't stop me now.
We need their help to find Rina.

260
00:16:02,633 --> 00:16:05,100
What are we going to do now?

261
00:16:05,233 --> 00:16:07,600
- I can't let her hurt my mom!
- We'll find them.

262
00:16:07,733 --> 00:16:09,500
We'll find them, okay?

263
00:16:11,100 --> 00:16:13,467
I need to find my mom.

264
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:17,167
Stay here. Stay with the baby.
Red and I will find them.

265
00:16:17,300 --> 00:16:18,300
You'll be safe here.

266
00:16:18,433 --> 00:16:19,633
No, Uncle.

267
00:16:19,767 --> 00:16:23,367
I have to be a good daughter
before I can be a good mother.

268
00:16:24,700 --> 00:16:28,433
I can't forgive myself
if my mom gets hurt.

269
00:16:28,567 --> 00:16:32,733
Please, Uncle, let me come
with you.

270
00:16:32,867 --> 00:16:35,900
Dad, I'll take care of Yenyen.

271
00:16:36,033 --> 00:16:38,067
I'll try to talk to mom.

272
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,800
She might change her mind.

273
00:16:40,933 --> 00:16:43,333
Where are you going to find her?

274
00:16:55,033 --> 00:16:58,300
- Hello?
- Yenyen, what's going on?

275
00:16:58,433 --> 00:17:00,100
Did you get your baby back?

276
00:17:00,233 --> 00:17:01,900
How's Amanda?

277
00:17:02,033 --> 00:17:03,400
Are you on your way home?

278
00:17:03,533 --> 00:17:04,467
Auntie.

279
00:17:04,600 --> 00:17:06,833
I've been praying
for you guys.

280
00:17:06,967 --> 00:17:09,067
I asked God to save both of you.

281
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:10,900
And your baby.

282
00:17:11,033 --> 00:17:14,633
Yen, please tell me
you're all safe. Please.

283
00:17:14,800 --> 00:17:17,433
Rina took my mom.

284
00:17:17,567 --> 00:17:18,700
What?

285
00:17:21,300 --> 00:17:25,867
My mom did everything
she could to get Chloe back.

286
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,833
Uncle Victor is on his way there
with the baby.

287
00:17:28,967 --> 00:17:31,600
Auntie, please take care of
Chloe.

288
00:17:32,633 --> 00:17:33,867
Why me?

289
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:36,067
What do I have to do?

290
00:17:37,333 --> 00:17:41,033
We're going to find them.
We're going to talk to Rina.

291
00:17:41,167 --> 00:17:43,467
And we'll save my mom.

292
00:17:46,833 --> 00:17:53,500
Auntie, please, promise me
you will take care of Chloe

293
00:17:53,667 --> 00:17:57,033
no matter what happens.

294
00:17:57,167 --> 00:17:58,633
Yen, what are you talking about?

295
00:17:58,767 --> 00:18:00,667
Don't talk like that.

296
00:18:01,833 --> 00:18:04,200
Auntie, please, promise me.

297
00:18:05,233 --> 00:18:08,500
Yenyen, what about Amanda?
What's going to happen to her?

298
00:18:20,033 --> 00:18:21,500
No one else should get hurt.

299
00:18:21,667 --> 00:18:23,000
You can be free again.

300
00:18:23,133 --> 00:18:25,400
No! Free? Me?

301
00:18:25,533 --> 00:18:27,200
I will be on the run
my whole life

302
00:18:27,333 --> 00:18:28,900
because the police
will keep chasing me.

303
00:18:29,033 --> 00:18:30,433
That's how things
will end for me.

304
00:18:30,567 --> 00:18:33,667
But you know what? I don't mind.

305
00:18:33,800 --> 00:18:36,700
As long I get my revenge
for Angelo.

306
00:19:30,033 --> 00:19:31,833
Amanda.

307
00:19:34,867 --> 00:19:37,267
You were able to get out
of jail...

308
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:42,033
You've changed your appearance.

309
00:19:43,967 --> 00:19:47,333
But you can never escape
my wrath.

310
00:19:49,533 --> 00:19:54,000
I will take you to hell!

311
00:20:10,667 --> 00:20:15,300
Angelo, my son.

312
00:20:17,967 --> 00:20:22,733
I'm sorry I didn't get
to visit you in a while.

313
00:20:24,867 --> 00:20:28,600
I have been rather preoccupied.

314
00:20:31,067 --> 00:20:33,333
I'm here now.

315
00:20:35,333 --> 00:20:37,833
To fulfill my promise.

316
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:45,767
I'm with the person
who did this to you.

317
00:20:47,367 --> 00:20:48,933
She's here now.

318
00:20:51,433 --> 00:20:55,900
She took your life.

319
00:20:57,567 --> 00:21:01,533
So she'll have to pay
for her life!

320
00:21:04,867 --> 00:21:08,900
Finally, son...

321
00:21:10,267 --> 00:21:12,900
I can get revenge for you now.

322
00:21:20,700 --> 00:21:22,467
You're crazy!

323
00:21:54,600 --> 00:21:55,433
Get out of here!

324
00:21:55,567 --> 00:21:56,667
You will get hurt too!

325
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:57,500
- Red!
- Mom.

326
00:21:57,633 --> 00:21:58,567
I won't leave you here.

327
00:21:58,700 --> 00:21:59,667
Get out of the way!

328
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:01,367
- Mom, please stop!
- Get out of the way!

329
00:22:01,500 --> 00:22:02,233
Stop this!

330
00:22:02,367 --> 00:22:04,500
Angelo won't like
this to happen!

331
00:22:04,633 --> 00:22:05,500
He will understand.

332
00:22:05,633 --> 00:22:08,600
He will understand
why I'm doing this.

333
00:22:08,733 --> 00:22:09,200
No!

334
00:22:09,333 --> 00:22:10,767
You can't be happy!

335
00:22:10,900 --> 00:22:13,667
- You can't!
- Stop this!
